channel.title: This is gay we have been taken over by noobs
channel.description:
:( I am sick of all these noobs going around like they think they know it all and they dont.
It is so stressful to get on and see ppl saying stuff like "i am a coder but i forgot how to do this bla bla bla bla bla........."
If the noobs really want to learn then let them learn but are we getting paid to teach tem no so why should we do it.
If they want to learn let them learn themselves or they can just stay the noobs they are. :D
